

Agenda : Creating the project using Mock data

Objectives : 

Creating the Angular project that perform CRUD operation for the Project management portal.The user should be able to perform add\delete\update\get the property details.

Tools :

- Angular 17

Modules :

- PropertyList
- PropertyCreate
- PropertyEdit
- PropertyDelete

Components :

ng g c PropertyList
ng g c PropertyCreate
ng g c PropertyEdit


Services :

ng generate service property 

Routing : 

const routes: Routes = [
  { path:'properties',component:PropertyListComponent },
  { path:'properties/create',component:PropertyCreateComponent },
  { path:'properties/edit/:id',component:PropertyEditComponent },
  {path:'',redirectTo:'/properties',pathMatch:'full'},
  
];

app.component.html:

<router-outlet></router-outlet>
